<p>I want to make single 301 redirect process for http to https and also trailing slash removal. </p>  <p><strong>http to https redirection method is</strong> </p>  <pre><code>RewriteCond %{SERVER_PORT} ^80$ RewriteRule (.*) https://%{SERVER_NAME}%{REQUEST_URI} [L,R=301] </code></pre>  <p><strong>Trailing slash removal method is</strong> </p>  <pre><code>RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d RewriteCond %{REQUEST_URI} (.+)/$ RewriteRule ^ %1 [R=301,L] </code></pre>  <p>I want both these steps in a single step, Is it possible?</p>